explanations.reason: The paper focuses on trends and factors associated with the utilization of allogeneic hematopoietic cell transplantation (alloHCT) among Medicare beneficiaries with acute myelogenous leukemia (AML). It discusses disparities in access to alloHCT and uses retrospective cohort study methods and logistic regression for analysis. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models in the title or abstract.
